* Requirements (Debian package name given in brackets)
  - Speech Dispatcher (speech-dispatcher)
  - Cotovia           (cotovia)
  - libdotconf        (libdotconf-dev)
  - libglib           (libglib2.0-dev)
  - libasound         (libasound2-dev)
 
* Build
  - Compile:
    make
  - Make debian package:
    make debian-package
   - This will generate the following deb package:
       ../cotovia-sd_version-number_arch.deb
       
